        life C5 THE STRAITS TIMES MONDAY, AUGUST 17, 2020 | | | • A monthly video series organised by
The Straits Times and the National Library Board you ask, we answer, come listen The Straits Times Managing Your Money during the Covid-19 Crisis Tan Ooi Boon Join The Straits Times’ Invest Editor and his guest, the chief executive of financial advisory firm SingCapita­l, as they discuss ways families can plan their finances to weather the current recession. These include the various government financial relief schemes that eligible Singaporea­ns can apply for as well as practical tips for households to manage their debts and incomes. They will also share why the pandemic has made prudent investment and retirement planning an essential task for all families. Mr Alfred Chia, The Straits Times Facebook Friday, Aug 28, 7pm Watch the video Tan Ooi Boon Alfred Chia Invest Editor,
The Straits Times Chief executive of financial advisory firm SingCapita­l Have a question for them?
